title: Episode 11: Chick-Fil-A, OIympics, and Guest Scott Olson!
description: How does our society associate brands with personal identity? After discussing Chick-Fil-A and dreaming about Epcot, guest Scott Olson, CEO of International Teams, joins the crew to talk about the changing face of world missions and social justice.
